                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1842" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0285</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8898 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">万事利的新丝绸之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Wensli: the New Silk New Road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">楼天阳，鲍贤玮等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">万事利公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">万事利；丝绸礼品；定制；丝绸装修；丝绸艺术品</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Wensli; Silk Gifts; Customization; Silk Decoration; Silk Collection</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例在简要回顾了中国丝绸的历史之后，描述了万事利公司从创业到成长，从二代继承创新“丝绸礼品”到谋划新丝绸业务的发展历程，并通过对万事利公司创二代李建华总裁的访谈详细介绍了丝绸礼品的开发背景、决策过程、以及营销战略实施的全过程。万事利公司将传统的丝绸材料与现代文化创意相结合，创造出“丝绸文化礼品”的新蓝海，为传统行业如何开创新品类，创造新市场，建设新品牌提供了弥足珍贵的经验。如今，万事利在曾经的蓝海业务丝绸礼品销售下降情况下，正致力于培育和决策下一个丝绸的蓝海，那么，丝绸礼品的成功经验能够复制到新的丝绸业务中去吗？李建华，又会在三个新兴丝绸业务（丝绸装修材料、丝绸精品服饰、丝绸收藏艺术品）中选择哪一个呢？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case reviews the history of silk in china, and describes the several key stages from the company building to development, the Second Entrepreneur Generation’s innovation of Silk Gifts and the recent planning of new Silk business in the whole development road of Wensli Co., Ltd. The case also discloses the market background、decision process and strategy execution of the innovative business of Silk Gifts by interviewing the CEO of Jianhua Li. Wensli has made extraordinary achievements in market innovation through redefined the silk from fabric materials to scarves as business gifts, which provides some management implication to creative new product category and blue ocean strategy. However, facing the sales sharply decreasing and fierce competitors of Silf Gifts business, the business innovation is becoming more and more imminent for Wensli’s future strategic development. In order to keep the market leader position, Mr. Li must make a strategic decision: how to develop three emerging business units, the Silk decorative materials, high-end boutique clothing and accessories, or artistic collections?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蓝海战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015-01</td>
                            </tr>
